<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Tabs - SURF Example</title>
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #eee;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: #00d4ff;
        }

        .tabs-container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .tab-buttons {
            display: flex;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .tab-btn {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 1rem;
            background: transparent;
            border: none;
            color: #666;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .tab-btn:hover {
            color: #999;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
        }

        .tab-btn[data-active="true"] {
            color: #00d4ff;
            background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
            border-bottom: 2px solid #00d4ff;
        }

        .tab-content {
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .tab-panel h3 {
            color: #7c3aed;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .tab-panel p {
            color: #999;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .back {
            position: fixed;
            top: 1rem;
            left: 1rem;
            color: #888;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .back:hover {
            color: #fff;
        }

        code {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: #888;
            text-align: left;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <a href="index.html" class="back">‚Üê Back</a>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Tabs Example</h1>

        <div class="tabs-container" d-cell="{ tab: 1 }">
            <div class="tab-buttons">
                <button class="tab-btn" d-signal="click: tab = 1" d-attr="data-active:tab == 1">
                    Overview
                </button>
                <button class="tab-btn" d-signal="click: tab = 2" d-attr="data-active:tab == 2">
                    Features
                </button>
                <button class="tab-btn" d-signal="click: tab = 3" d-attr="data-active:tab == 3">
                    Pricing
                </button>
            </div>

            <div class="tab-content">
                <div class="tab-panel" d-show="tab == 1">
                    <h3>Overview</h3>
                    <p>SURF is an HTML-first framework that puts the server in control. The client handles only local,
                        temporary interactions like these tabs.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tab-panel" d-show="tab == 2">
                    <h3>Features</h3>
                    <p>Surfaces for server-driven updates. Cells for local state. Signals for reactivity. Pulses for
                        server communication. Echo for state preservation.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tab-panel" d-show="tab == 3">
                    <h3>Pricing</h3>
                    <p>SURF is open source and free forever. No hidden costs, no premium tiers, no vendor lock-in.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <code>
&lt;div d-cell="{ tab: 1 }"&gt;
  &lt;button d-signal="click: tab = 1" d-attr="data-active:tab == 1"&gt;Tab 1&lt;/button&gt;
  &lt;div d-show="tab == 1"&gt;Content 1&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
    </code>
    </div>

    <script src="/dist/surf.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>